            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Hd1e108">Rubrica 8</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De credito et debito</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="66"/>
      ¶ De credito et debito. Rubrica. 8
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-d1e119">
               <lb ed="#V" n="67"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Rd1e115">PSalmista 36 pslamus.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Qd1e123">
               Mu<lb ed="#V" n="68" break="no"/>tuabitur 
               pec<lb ed="#V" n="69" break="no"/>cator: et non soluet.</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-d1e131">
               <lb ed="#V" n="70"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Rd1e129">Salomon in prouerbiis. ca. 6.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Qd1e135">
               Si<lb ed="#V" n="71" break="no"/>spoponderis pro amico tuo: defixisti apud
        <lb ed="#V" n="72"/>extraneum animam tuam: illaqueatus es 
               ver<lb ed="#V" n="73" break="no"/>bis oris tui: et captus propriis sermonibus
        <lb ed="#V" n="74"/>tuis. Fac ergo quod dico: temetipsum 
               libe<lb ed="#V" n="75" break="no"/>ra: quia incidisti in manus proximi tui: 
               discur<lb ed="#V" n="76" break="no"/>re festina: amicum tuum suscita: ne dederis 
               som<lb ed="#V" n="77" break="no"/>num oculis tuis: nec dormitent palpebre tue
        <lb ed="#V" n="78"/>erue quasi damula de manum: et quasi auis de
        <lb ed="#V" n="79"/>insidiis aucupis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-d1e159"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Rd1e157">22 c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Qd1e161">Qui accipit mutuum
        <lb ed="#V" n="80"/>seruus est fenerantis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-d1e167">
               <lb ed="#V" n="81"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Rd1e169">Iesus filius sirach in eccl. c. 29</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Qd1e171">Fenerare
        <lb ed="#V" n="82"/>tibi proximo in tempore necessitatis illius. 
               Red<lb ed="#V" n="83" break="no"/>de proximo in tempore suo. Multi non causa 
               ne<lb ed="#V" n="84" break="no"/>quitie: non fenerati sunt: sed fraudari gratis
        <lb ed="#V" n="85"/>timuerunt. Uir bonus fidem facit proximo suo.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-d1e183">
               <lb ed="#V" n="86"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Rd1e187">Mattheus in euangelio. c. 22.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Qd1e187">Reddite quae sunt
        <lb ed="#V" n="87"/>cesaris cesari: et que sunt dei deo.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-d1e193"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Rd1e197">Idem 
               di<lb ed="#V" n="88" break="no"/>cit marcus in euangelio. c. 11.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Qd1e195"/>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-d1e201"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Rd1e207">Idem dicit
        <lb ed="#V" n="89"/>lucas in euangelio. c. 20</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Qd1e203"> <!--127.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="50-v"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
               </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-d1e215">
               <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Rd1e226">P&gt;aulus apostolus epistola ad roma. c. 13</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Qd1e219">
               Reddi<lb ed="#V" n="2" break="no"/>te omnibus debita: cui tribulum tributum: cui
        <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>vectigal vectigal: cui honorem honorem.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-d1e228">
               <lb ed="#V" n="4"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Rd1e241">Seneca epistolarum ad lucillum li. 3. e. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Qd1e232">
               Le<lb ed="#V" n="5" break="no"/>ue es alienum debitorem facit: graue inimicum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-d1e238">
               <lb ed="#V" n="6"/> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Rd1e253">Idem in prouerb.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Qd1e242">Es alienum homini 
               in<lb ed="#V" n="7" break="no"/>genuo: acerba seruitus est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-d1e248">
               <lb ed="#V" n="8"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Rd1e265">Lex diges. ti. de verb. sig. l. sub signatum.
        <lb ed="#V" n="9"/>§. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Qd1e252">Bona intelliguntur cuiusque qua deducto ere
        <lb ed="#V" n="10"/>alieno supersunt.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-d1e260">
               <lb ed="#V" n="11"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Rd1e280">Cato. c. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Qd1e264">Mutuum da. Cui des videto.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-d1e268">
               <lb ed="#V" n="12"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Rd1e290">Boetius de disciplina scholarium li. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Qd1e272">
               De<lb ed="#V" n="13" break="no"/>clamatione creditorum: nihil amarius 
               men<lb ed="#V" n="14" break="no"/>ti imprimitur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-d1e280">
               <lb ed="#V" n="15"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Rd1e304">Cassiodorus epistolarum lib. 12. et fi. e. 2.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="16"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Qd1e284">Irrite suspenditur quod nullis protractionibus
        <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>euitatur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-d1e293"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Rd1e316">10. e.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Qd1e295">Reatus quidam est esse sub
        <lb ed="#V" n="18"/>debito: nec liber potest veraciter dici qui 
               pro<lb ed="#V" n="19" break="no"/>batur obnoxius reperiri.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-d1e303"> /
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Rd1e328">16. e.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Qd1e305">Debitum si
        <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>quidem quod non potest euitari: prona 
               de<lb ed="#V" n="21" break="no"/>bet mente semper offerri: vt fiat beneficium quod
        <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>sine compulsione constat illatum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-d1e315">
               <lb ed="#V" n="23"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Rd1e344">Iacobus beneuentanus. c. 35.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Qd1e319">Nolo quod
        <lb ed="#V" n="24"/>prestes fili tua litigiosis.
        <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>Aut illis et qui sibi semper egent.
        <lb ed="#V" n="26"/>Credita vix etenim vel nunquam reddere curant.
        <lb ed="#V" n="27"/>Consueuere tamen reddere verba pia.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-d1e331">
               <lb ed="#V" n="28"/>
             ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Rd1e362">Prouerb. vulgar:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d38247-Qd1e335">Mal compra clesura chi
        <lb ed="#V" n="29"/>tol dinari a osura.
        <lb ed="#V" n="30"/>El debito destruze chin vnca nol fuze.
        <lb ed="#V" n="31"/>Uolce elaltrum apprendere et amaro parer a
        <lb ed="#V" n="32"/>rendere.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
